1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:06,520
To start this body scan, sit in an alert position or lie down.

2
00:00:10,540 --> 00:00:15,660
When your mind wanders, gently bring it back to the words being spoken,

3
00:00:15,660 --> 00:00:20,760
returning to whatever is youâ€™re being asked to be aware of.

4
00:00:20,760 --> 00:00:26,560
Practice non-judgment, practice acceptance.

5
00:00:28,720 --> 00:00:37,200
Begin by closing your eyes, or by finding a place on the floor in front of you to gently rest your gaze.

6
00:00:41,640 --> 00:00:46,340
Now gently turn your attention to your toes.

7
00:00:46,840 --> 00:00:51,840
Wiggle them for just a moment to help you get your focus there.

8
00:00:57,260 --> 00:01:03,220
Now slowly begin to scan from your toes to the bottom of your feet,

9
00:01:03,740 --> 00:01:08,660
feeling the balls and the arches and the heels.

10
00:01:17,620 --> 00:01:23,000
Now circle your attention around to the top of your feet,

11
00:01:23,160 --> 00:01:28,600
taking a moment to notice that you can sense that area of your body.

12
00:01:28,860 --> 00:01:33,460
You can be aware of the top of your feet.

13
00:01:42,980 --> 00:01:46,980
Begin to scan further up to the ankles,

14
00:01:47,340 --> 00:01:53,460
taking a moment to notice the sensation that is present at the ankles.

15
00:01:55,940 --> 00:01:59,700
It may be one ankle first and then the other,

16
00:01:59,800 --> 00:02:04,100
just gently be aware of any sensations you notice here.

17
00:02:15,580 --> 00:02:19,840
Now, gently scan up to your calves,

18
00:02:19,980 --> 00:02:26,760
becoming aware of your calves and noticing any sensations that you experience here.

19
00:02:42,180 --> 00:02:45,300
It may be one calf first and then the other,

20
00:02:45,480 --> 00:02:48,100
just gently be aware

21
00:02:50,640 --> 00:02:53,380
noticing sensation at the calves.

22
00:03:03,340 --> 00:03:09,840
Then wrap your attention around to the front of your lower legs, taking a moment to notice your shins,

23
00:03:14,040 --> 00:03:19,400
be aware of any sensations that you experience here.

24
00:03:32,220 --> 00:03:36,400
Scanning further up, place your attention on your knees,

25
00:03:41,560 --> 00:03:46,060
notice any experience at your knees

26
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:07,000
and then gently scanning upward, move to your thighs,

27
00:04:08,160 --> 00:04:12,180
feeling the sensation at your thighs.

28
00:04:19,060 --> 00:04:25,560
Notice that you can experience sensation wherever you place your attention,

29
00:04:25,680 --> 00:04:30,780
even if the sensation is soft and barely detectable.

30
00:04:39,660 --> 00:04:46,920
And now, shifting your attention again, gently circle around to the backs of your legs,

31
00:04:47,100 --> 00:04:51,020
feeling the area of your quadriceps,

32
00:04:51,020 --> 00:04:55,660
noticing any sensation at the back of your legs.

33
00:05:11,420 --> 00:05:16,360
Now gently scan up to your hips,

34
00:05:16,360 --> 00:05:22,320
feeling the bend of your hips or the position of the hips if you are lying down.

35
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:31,160
Notice any sensations, any experiences that arise here.

36
00:05:51,460 --> 00:05:55,480
Now gently scan around to your lower back,

37
00:05:55,480 --> 00:06:00,380
feeling any sensation in that area of your body,

38
00:06:01,180 --> 00:06:04,860
being aware of your lower back.

39
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:31,500
Now gently scan around to the front of your body, becoming aware of your abdomen,

40
00:06:32,520 --> 00:06:39,000
noticing any sensations that you experience here.

41
00:06:39,820 --> 00:06:43,980
Now scanning upward, notice your stomach,

42
00:06:44,380 --> 00:06:49,200
gently placing your attention on the area of your stomach,

43
00:06:49,200 --> 00:06:55,400
noticing all that rises and falls, all that you experience.

44
00:07:01,500 --> 00:07:07,060
Now gently scanning higher, become aware of your chest.

45
00:07:08,380 --> 00:07:12,820
Notice how it rises and falls as you breathe,

46
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:19,160
gently allow yourself to be aware of each sensation of the chest.

47
00:07:33,900 --> 00:07:37,520
Now gently circle around to the middle of your back,

48
00:07:37,700 --> 00:07:43,460
paying attention to whatever you experience as you notice the middle of your back.

49
00:08:01,160 --> 00:08:07,760
Now gently scanning upward, notice the area of your upper back and shoulder blades.

50
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:14,060
Gently rest your attention on this part of your body.

51
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:28,580
Scan out across your shoulders, noticing any sensation that arises here,

52
00:08:28,600 --> 00:08:32,760
any experience that you become aware of.

53
00:08:43,820 --> 00:08:50,680
Gently move your attention to your upper arms, noticing the area of the biceps.

54
00:08:56,020 --> 00:09:00,520
Be aware that you can feel sensation here,

55
00:09:01,040 --> 00:09:03,200
simply noticing.

56
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:21,460
Now wrapping around to the back of your arms, notice the area of the triceps.

57
00:09:24,820 --> 00:09:30,980
Notice that you can experience sensation on the upper part and backside of your arms.

58
00:09:45,020 --> 00:09:50,460
Scanning further, move your attention to your elbows,

59
00:09:50,540 --> 00:09:54,680
noticing any sensation that you experience here,

60
00:09:55,860 --> 00:09:59,240
noticing the bend if your elbows are bent,

61
00:09:59,520 --> 00:10:03,620
or notice what it feels like if your arms are straight.

62
00:10:04,220 --> 00:10:08,640
Simply be aware of sensation at your elbows.

63
00:10:24,800 --> 00:10:32,180
Now gently scan down to your lower arm, noticing the tops of your lower arms.

64
00:10:45,120 --> 00:10:47,980
And then gently circle around to the bottom,

65
00:10:47,980 --> 00:10:53,120
noticing the area at the bottom of your lower arms.

66
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:11,660
Now scanning further, gently move to your wrists,

67
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:18,280
simply being aware of any sensation that you experience here.

68
00:11:18,420 --> 00:11:21,160
It may be one wrist and then the other,

69
00:11:21,280 --> 00:11:26,220
simply be aware of the sensation at your wrists.

70
00:11:36,660 --> 00:11:40,640
Scan further out to the palms of your hands,

71
00:11:40,660 --> 00:11:46,640
becoming aware of any sensation that you experience at the palms.

72
00:11:49,780 --> 00:11:54,060
Notice your palms as your hands gently rest.

73
00:12:03,760 --> 00:12:06,680
And then gently scan to the fingers,

74
00:12:06,760 --> 00:12:09,740
noticing any sensation at the knuckles

75
00:12:09,740 --> 00:12:16,280
or any other experiences that arise as you turn your attention here.

76
00:12:22,240 --> 00:12:25,500
Scan right out to the tips of your fingers,

77
00:12:25,620 --> 00:12:30,520
noticing any sensation at the tips of your fingers.

78
00:12:47,480 --> 00:12:52,240
Now gently releasing your attention from the tips of your fingers,

79
00:12:52,420 --> 00:12:55,840
place your attention on the base of your neck.

80
00:12:57,980 --> 00:13:01,840
Begin to scan upward, noticing your neck,

81
00:13:02,020 --> 00:13:05,700
and then the base and back of your head.

82
00:13:13,300 --> 00:13:17,240
Now gently scan around to the front of your head,

83
00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:20,640
becoming aware of your chin.

84
00:13:24,360 --> 00:13:28,060
Gently place your attention at the chin,

85
00:13:28,060 --> 00:13:32,820
being aware of any sensation you experience here.

86
00:13:44,480 --> 00:13:49,980
Begin to slowly scan upward, noticing your lips,

87
00:13:52,720 --> 00:13:55,260
your nose,

88
00:13:55,680 --> 00:13:58,280
your cheeks,

89
00:14:00,780 --> 00:14:03,520
your eyes,

90
00:14:05,280 --> 00:14:07,800
your forehead,

91
00:14:11,440 --> 00:14:16,240
and then continue scanning upward right to the top of your scalp,

92
00:14:16,340 --> 00:14:22,600
becoming aware of the sensation that you experience right at the top of your head.

93
00:14:33,040 --> 00:14:38,200
Now gently releasing your attention from the sensation at the top of your head,

94
00:14:38,400 --> 00:14:44,820
take a moment and notice your whole body sitting in the chair or lying down.

95
00:14:48,760 --> 00:14:53,140
Be aware of the sensations of pressure,

96
00:14:53,140 --> 00:15:01,280
noticing where your body touches the chair

97
00:15:01,340 --> 00:15:05,020
and noticing where it does not touch.

98
00:15:18,160 --> 00:15:21,800
Now releasing your attention from your body,

99
00:15:21,800 --> 00:15:27,060
gently place your attention on the image of the room that you are in,

100
00:15:30,480 --> 00:15:36,100
and when you are ready, open your eyes.

101
00:15:39,800 --> 00:15:43,640
Thank you for doing this body scan awareness exercise.

